Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:12.97,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 请
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:19.01,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,是第10签
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:21.22,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同学要不要抽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:25.49,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:26.34,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.39,0:09:31.06,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,是大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.22,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:33.77,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:36.26,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,第16签
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.78,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 折木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:46.89,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:49.78,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,看来今年会有好事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs14\bord0\be1\shad0}末吉：一般而言，是除了凶以及大凶以外最不好的签
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:52.91,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你抽到末吉了吧
